{"tid":2445681,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"比特幣漲破6萬美元 再創新高","createTime":"2021-03-13T21:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T04:38:13.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8591ad5763dbcd4b1ffa1ccc5bd0712d23c8f1a4","tid":2445681,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T21:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Sdd1VVPvG8ZQFkckVNp2oQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTQyMDtoPTI3Mi41NzE0Mjg1NzE0Mjg1NjtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/xrqG_QvIAQgHVaYUIMzJ4Q--~B/aD0xNTk7dz0yNDU7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/afp.com.hk/6008b32a9759e16c63cfeefd47ad8b4d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FSdd1VVPvG8ZQFkckVNp2oQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTQyMDtoPTI3Mi41NzE0Mjg1NzE0Mjg1NjtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FxrqG_QvIAQgHVaYUIMzJ4Q--~B%2FaD0xNTk7dz0yNDU7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fafp.com.hk%2F6008b32a9759e16c63cfeefd47ad8b4d&h=cb1d2127&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（法新社巴黎13日電） 由於愈來愈多重量級企業支持全球最受歡迎虛擬貨幣比特幣（Bitcoin），帶動比特幣價位水漲船高，比特幣今天一度短暫漲破6萬美元（約新台幣169萬元）。<br />\n<br />\n根據追蹤比特幣價格網站CoinMarketCap，台北晚間7時49分，比特幣衝上6萬12美元，創下空前新高。<br />\n<br />\n在線支付平台PayPal曾稱，PayPal將同意用戶使用比特幣交易，激勵比特幣自去年3月價位站上5000美元以來持續飆升。<br />\n<br />\n2009年發行的比特幣，在2017年元月價位不到1000美元，同年12月漲至近2萬美元而聲名大噪。"},{"pid":"894c3bd6e24c1d88ebc581e79ae480e7e70897c2","tid":2445681,"uid":23061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T21:44:29.000Z","msg":"多謝連登users燈到60000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b59eab2ed6b22d51c43bf348959c3643c5d9ab","tid":2445681,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"894c3bd6e24c1d88ebc581e79ae480e7e70897c2","tid":2445681,"uid":23061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T21:44:29.000Z","msg":"多謝連登users燈到60000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.